{"tid":1193143,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"仲諗緊聽日出唔出嘅人唔該入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-06-08T18:33:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T18:53:09.000Z","uid":205565,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"251b2cb9f211c6ad7a2520081d40bbbd3cf53ebb","tid":1193143,"uid":205565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T18:33:14.000Z","msg":"條路自己揀 仆街唔好喊<br />\n<br />\n事到如今到底你地幾時先意識到問題嘅嚴重性<br />\n到底仲要避到幾時？<br />\n而家唔係你口口聲聲話反對啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做野啦柒頭！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得把口你做乜都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係到時你把口仲可以講到幾多野啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你以為你咩都唔做就可以有收穫？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你以為你翹埋雙手都有人幫你解決問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成功唔係靠把口 更加唔係靠人地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好簡單一個道理 你唔付出係一定冇收穫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一直匿埋喺電腦到面 你仲想匿到幾時？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪要到咩都冇得匿個時 ？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你先肯選擇出嚟啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時仲會有幾多人仲係到啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n醒下啦柒頭！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你今日係屋企hea！<br />\n你聽日就可能係上面！<br />\n你今日決定為自己發聲！<br />\n你聽日就為自己帶來自由！<br />\n<br />\n當你所做嘅野都被人監控<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當你想發聲但有所限制時<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n太遲啦..一切都太遲啦&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你睇下上面班「人」？<br />\n有幾多「人」仲可以暢所欲言？<br />\n係偉大嘅統治下，每一句說話都要你諗清諗楚！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次一齊出嚟 ！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同所有「香港人」一齊打呢場仗！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好等到物是人非，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港變成香港市個時你先嚟後悔啦好嗎&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢五年間香港已經失去左好多野了&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求下你地唔好等香港失去更多個時&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n先識得醒覺&hellip;到個時所有野都太遲啦&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n已經係冇可能再挽回架啦&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲諗緊出唔出嚟嘅人&hellip;<br />\n我求下你地唔好再浪費時間諗啦！<br />\n我好肯定你最後嘅決定&hellip;<br />\n你最後嘅選擇&hellip;會係乜野！！<br />\n<br />\n呢條條路係你自己揀嘅<br />\n出左事你後悔都冇用啦<br />\n出嚟啦香港人<br />\n唔好再逃避了<br />\n面對現實吧啦<br />\n愛惜你嘅「香港」！"},{"pid":"0ab7f4b19d287679d3198da52572e3fc7bdfa35d","tid":1193143,"uid":65439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T18:36:07.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e3cfaa9f1151d136aa4b1e061b3fd4e40c0dbca","tid":1193143,"uid":130406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T18:42:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1a022f103dfbaf9f82d8f053e620251ee30eec6b","tid":1193143,"uid":205565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T18:42:38.000Z","msg":"做左咁耐cdrom嘅你 出嚟啦<br />\n一齊嚟改寫命運啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a54109c384bcf0f17929867f3bae8dc53a4cf8b7","tid":1193143,"uid":204788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T18:53:09.000Z","msg":"幫推"}]}